<body>
Reports entity listener classes without any entity listener methods.

<p><b>Example:</b></p><br/>
<pre><code lang="java">
  @Entity
  @EntityListeners(value = JavaEntityListener.class)
  public class JavaEntity { ... }

  class JavaEntityListener { // Error: no entity listener-specific methods found

  }
</code></pre>
</body>
